J. C. Steele, Plaintiff in Error, v. J. W. Baggett, et al., Defendants in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Okaloosa. T. A. James, for Plaintiff in Error; Daniel Campbell & Son, for Defendants in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for defendants in error.
